PDef_CodeSnippets.Comment:
============================================================
TASK MONITORING
============================================================
Each Task has its own monitoring instruction (L_TaskMon AOI).
However, a Task cannot monitor its own "Task Inhibited" status,
because the AOI is not scanned if its Task is Inhibited!

So this small Task is used to monitor each of the other
controller Tasks and set the "TaskInhibited" Status
of those Tasks if they are set Inhibited.

Each rung below monitors the Inhibited status of
one of this controller's Tasks.
